        <scopecontent>
            <p>Includes city contracts, 1850-1915, for such work as dredging the Buffalo River, canal dredging, street lighting, and bridge construction; accounts and claims, 1863-1875, and powers of attorney and other documents, 1909-1910, concerning improving Elmwood Ave. and Morgan St.</p>
        <arrangement>
                <p>Organized into three series: I. Contracts, 1850-1915. II. Accounts and claims, 1863-1875. III. Streets improvement documents, 1909- 1910. Chronological arrangement by year within series.</p>
            </arrangement>
        </scopecontent>
